title: Bug 132103 - No objects under Context in palette when scripting a data set
description: When scripting a data set, there are no objects under Context in the palette.
OB: No objects are displayed under Context in the palette when scripting a data set.
EB: Expected behavior is that relevant objects under Context should be visible in the palette during scripting.
SR:
1. Open the scripting interface for a data set.
2. Navigate to the palette and check for objects under the 'Context' section.
3. Observe that no objects are displayed.
